### Overview and Deliverables

Homework 1 is due this Sunday at midnight

### Learning Objectives

* Solving unconstrained least squares problems
  - Properties of the Gram matrix and the pseudoinverse
* Applications:
  - Optimization 
  - Linear Regression
  - Function Fitting


### Readings

Chapter 12 and 13 of [Introduction to Applied Linear Algebra](https://web.stanford.edu/~boyd/vmls/vmls.pdf)



